{"lastModified":1763459407047,"uri":"c::7819240034::vessel::a06bf890-b978-11f0-8dbd-bd5dc8416ab1","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nThe Bali 5.2 is a premium sailing catamaran built for those who seek space, comfort, and adventure at sea. Its innovative open-space design connects the saloon, galley, and cockpit on a single level, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor experience. The solid foredeck with a spacious lounge replaces traditional trampolines, providing a comfortable area for relaxation, sunbathing, and socializing.\n\nThe flybridge is another standout feature, offering panoramic views and extra seating, making it an ideal spot to enjoy the journey. With 5- or 6-cabin layouts, each with an en-suite bathroom, the Bali 5.2 ensures privacy and comfort for all guests, making it a perfect choice for yacht charters in Greece.\n\nDesigned for extended cruising, it boasts large fuel and water capacities, advanced refrigeration, and energy autonomy, allowing for longer journeys without compromise. Whether exploring the Greek islands or enjoying a relaxing getaway, the Bali 5.2 offers the ultimate sailing experience.","blueprint":{"name":"LEFKAS - KOS 52.CAT3","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::a06bf890-b978-11f0-8dbd-bd5dc8416ab1::assets::8cb74670-b97c-11f0-ad23-c7d6830b7c8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a06bf890-b978-11f0-8dbd-bd5dc8416ab1::assets::8c7c6050-b97c-11f0-9305-6db2388e4811/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a06bf890-b978-11f0-8dbd-bd5dc8416ab1::assets::8c7cfc90-b97c-11f0-9305-6db2388e4811/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a06bf890-b978-11f0-8dbd-bd5dc8416ab1::assets::8c7e0e00-b97c-11f0-ad23-c7d6830b7c8a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a06bf890-b978-11f0-8dbd-bd5dc8416ab1::assets::8caf3020-b97c-11f0-9305-6db2388e4811/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::a06bf890-b978-11f0-8dbd-bd5dc8416ab1::assets::8cb809c0-b97c-11f0-9305-6db2388e